  "notes": "Live Shopify Admin 2026-04 evidence for two protected-definition guards. Standard-template product subtitle definitions reject edits to name, description, and validations with INVALID_INPUT while preserving the original definition. App-reserved namespaces created through `$app:<suffix>` reject metafieldDefinitionDelete without deleteAllAssociatedMetafields, return RESERVED_NAMESPACE_ORPHANED_METAFIELDS, retain the definition, and delete successfully when the flag is true."
